    "text": "<@U021D0Q3LDB> I find “token” a spot-on term for it (<https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lexical_analysis#Token|https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lexical_analysis#Token>) and would say that “tag” is overused. But… well… as far as I can tell, I’m probably double your age and therefore “old school”. ;-)",
